OL,6,FA scheme for baby loss certificates
OL,7,Fhas been extended. ITV News Presenter
OL,8,FLucrezia Millarini spoke to Emily
OL,9,FCleary, who had a miscarriage in 2014,
OL,10,Fand Vicki Robinson, Miscarriage
OL,11,FAssociation Chief Executive
OL,13,FMore parents who have experienced the
OL,14,Floss of a baby early in pregnancy will
OL,15,Fnow be able to apply to have their
OL,16,Fchild's life officially recognised by
OL,17,Fa certificate.
