OL,3,CMore parents eligible for certificate
OL,4,Crecognising pregnancy loss
OL,6,FThe government has announced it will
OL,7,Fextend the baby loss certificate
OL,8,Fscheme, which was launched in February
OL,9,Ffor those who have experienced a loss
OL,10,Fsince September 2018.
OL,12,FThere will now be no time limit on the
OL,13,Finitiative, with certificates
OL,14,Favailable for any parent who has
OL,15,Fexperienced a loss before 24 weeks, or
OL,16,F28 weeks if the loss occurred before
OL,17,FOctober 1992.
