OL,16,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said
OL,17,Fthat losing a pregnancy can be "deeply
OL,18,Fdistressing", and added: "There is so
OL,19,Fmuch love and so many dreams for the
OL,20,Ffuture wrapped up in a tiny life".
