OL,3,CMore parents eligible for certificate
OL,4,Crecognising pregnancy loss
OL,6,F"That's why it is important for
OL,7,Fbereaved parents to have the option to
OL,8,Fofficially recognise the existence of
OL,9,Ftheir babies and how much they matter.
OL,10,FI'm pleased we can now ensure all
OL,11,Fparents are able to apply for these
OL,12,Fcertificates, no matter how long ago
OL,13,Fthey lost their pregnancies," he said.
OL,15,FVicki Robinson, chief executive of the
OL,16,Fcharity Miscarriage Association, said
OL,17,Fthe move marks "a significant
OL,18,Fmilestone" for people waiting for this
OL,19,Frecognition.
