OL,6,F"For many, even the earliest of losses
OL,7,Fcan be deeply distressing, both
OL,8,Femotionally and physically, but having
OL,9,Fa formal acknowledgement as a marker
OL,10,Fof their loss can be a meaningful part
OL,11,Fof the grieving process.
OL,13,F"We know from the people that we
OL,14,Fsupport how much the certification
OL,15,Fscheme has helped those who have
OL,16,Fexperienced pregnancy loss, so this is
OL,17,Fgreat news that people whose losses
OL,18,Fwere previously not acknowledged now
OL,19,Fcan be."
