OL,6,FThe baby loss certificate scheme was
OL,7,Fformed following the recommendations
OL,8,Fof the independent Pregnancy Loss
OL,9,FReview, which was published in 2023.
OL,11,FTo request a baby loss certificate
OL,12,Fvisit www.gov.uk/request-baby-loss-
OL,13,Fcertificate
OL,15,FSamantha Collinge, bereavement lead
OL,16,Fmidwife at George Eliot Hospital NHS
OL,17,FTrust and co-chair of the Pregnancy
OL,18,FLoss Review, described the extension
OL,19,Fas a "huge milestone moment".
